From a37fe583fb9838b414b262d71f6594c97161a67e Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Brian Neradt <brian.neradt@gmail.com>
Date: Fri, 18 Jun 2021 13:11:12 -0500
Subject: [PATCH] Revert "Do not invalidate cached resources upon error
 responses to unsafe methods (#7864)" (#7954)

This reverts commit c75c797410a8661f23ce1b9868b771457b1026f7.

This change introduces a failure in the esi AuTest. I'll revert this now
to free up CI and circle back around on the patch later.
---
